      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON CURRENCY (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.39) at this track behind Saint Finnie in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Good form should continue. SEATS TWO (1) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 6 lengths into third (22.85) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Racing well and deserves a win. MORAINE GRACE (7) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing third and beaten a neck (22.40) behind Ollie Deeds at this track. Hard to beat again. DUKE CABOOM (4) has ability and can find the frame.",
